{"tid":1958231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[世界末日] 飛田新地自肅停止營業，違者除名處分","createTime":"2020-04-04T12:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T13:16:06.000Z","uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d048aef9f6d00598d61b8efe2175babd88e5770","tid":1958231,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Xv8p1Tk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXv8p1Tk.png&h=20d0c6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KCESuw7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKCESuw7.png&h=ab6a178e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼上個月31號宣布因疫情而希望各料理店暫停營業之後<br />\n<br />\n管理飛田新地嘅組織喺 3 號出咗篇嘢明令禁止再有料理店繼續營業<br />\n<br />\n註：除名，破門都係日本黑道常用嘅處罰方法<br />\n破門同除名相近，都係將人逐出黑道家門，但破門之後尚有機會返返嚟，而除名就基本上當係二五仔咁對待，可能變咗仇人"},{"pid":"60bcdc32f2fbbad85555f77974b33437319847c5","tid":1958231,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:00:41.000Z","msg":"睇除名. 以為封信係政府. <br />\n盜亦有道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f9428b8070dbf06327aca0907a2b4540500b0f","tid":1958231,"uid":288537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b9b0cd359d9140496abf2a03be899273ff45a7a","tid":1958231,"uid":247402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"日本黑幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b84a11003fb9606f675e2ee2e6c5da271473da","tid":1958231,"uid":164497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"真正做野抗疫既黑幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56d0537452c8ce14fdab970f3a074b4888c28e4","tid":1958231,"uid":25952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"相反睇下姓向個條撚樣<br />\n搵少陣錢都屌晒鬼"},{"pid"